{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Eph|1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","chapter":1,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v11","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":1,"text":"Paul, an apostle of Christ Jesus by God’s will: To the faithful saints in Christ Jesus at Ephesus.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":2,"text":"Grace to you and peace from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":3,"text":"Blessed is the God and Father of our Lord Jesus Christ, who has blessed us with every spiritual blessing in the heavens in Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":4,"text":"For he chose us in him, before the foundation of the world, to be holy and blameless in love before him.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":5,"text":"He predestined us to be adopted as sons through Jesus Christ for himself, according to the good pleasure of his will,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":6,"text":"to the praise of his glorious grace that he lavished on us in the Beloved One.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":7,"text":"In him we have redemption through his blood, the forgiveness of our trespasses, according to the riches of his grace","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":8,"text":"that he richly poured out on us with all wisdom and understanding.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":9,"text":"He made known to us the mystery of his will, according to his good pleasure that he purposed in Christ","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":10,"text":"as a plan for the right time —to bring everything together in Christ, both things in heaven and things on earth in him.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":11,"text":"In him we have also received an inheritance, because we were predestined according to the plan of the one who works out everything in agreement with the purpose of his will,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":12,"text":"so that we who had already put our hope in Christ might bring praise to his glory.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":13,"text":"In him you also were sealed with the promised Holy Spirit when you heard the word of truth, the gospel of your salvation, and when you believed.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":14,"text":"The Holy Spirit is the down payment of our inheritance, until the redemption of the possession, to the praise of his glory.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":15,"text":"This is why, since I heard about your faith in the Lord Jesus and your love for all the saints,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":16,"text":"I never stop giving thanks for you as I remember you in my prayers.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":17,"text":"I pray that the God of our Lord Jesus Christ, the glorious Father, would give you the Spirit of wisdom and revelation in the knowledge of him.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":18,"text":"I pray that the eyes of your heart may be enlightened so that you may know what is the hope of his calling, what is the wealth of his glorious inheritance in the saints,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":19,"text":"and what is the immeasurable greatness of his power toward us who believe, according to the mighty working of his strength.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":20,"text":"He exercised this power in Christ by raising him from the dead and seating him at his right hand in the heavens —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":21,"text":"far above every ruler and authority, power and dominion, and every title given, not only in this age but also in the one to come.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:22","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":22,"text":"And he subjected everything under his feet and appointed him as head over everything for the church,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:23","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":1,"verse":23,"text":"which is his body, the fullness of the one who fills all things in every way.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","chapter":1,"paragraphStarts":[1,2,3,7,11,13,15,20],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"Greeting"},{"beforeVerse":3,"text":"God’s Rich Blessings"},{"beforeVerse":15,"text":"Prayer for Spiritual Insight"},{"beforeVerse":20,"text":"God’s Power in Christ"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Paul, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 13:9","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" an apostle of Christ Jesus by God’s will: "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 1:9","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" To the faithful saints "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 5:2","book":"Eph","chapter":5,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" in Christ Jesus "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or to the saints, the believers in Christ Jesus"},{"kind":"text","text":" at Ephesus. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss omit at Ephesus"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 18:19–21","book":"Act","chapter":18,"verse":19,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 19:9–10","book":"Act","chapter":19,"verse":9,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 20:3","book":"Act","chapter":20,"verse":3,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 20:17","book":"Act","chapter":20,"verse":17,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 15:32","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":32,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 2:1","book":"Rev","chapter":2,"verse":1,"letter":"g"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 13:9","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":9},{"label":"Eph 1:9","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":9},{"label":"Eph 5:2","book":"Eph","chapter":5,"verse":2},{"label":"Ac 18:19–21","book":"Act","chapter":18,"verse":19},{"label":"Ac 19:9–10","book":"Act","chapter":19,"verse":9},{"label":"Ac 20:3","book":"Act","chapter":20,"verse":3},{"label":"Ac 20:17","book":"Act","chapter":20,"verse":17},{"label":"1Co 15:32","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":32},{"label":"Rv 2:1","book":"Rev","chapter":2,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or to the saints, the believers in Christ Jesus"},{"marker":2,"text":"Other mss omit at Ephesus"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Grace to you and peace from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Blessed is the God and Father of our Lord Jesus Christ, who has blessed us with every spiritual blessing in the heavens in Christ. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 1:20","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":20,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 2:6","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 3:10","book":"Eph","chapter":3,"verse":10,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 6:12","book":"Eph","chapter":6,"verse":12,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Eph 1:20","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":20},{"label":"Eph 2:6","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":6},{"label":"Eph 3:10","book":"Eph","chapter":3,"verse":10},{"label":"Eph 6:12","book":"Eph","chapter":6,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For he chose us in him, before the foundation of the world, to be holy and blameless in love before him. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or in his sight. In love"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jd 1:24","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":24,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jd 1:24","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":24}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or in his sight. In love"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He predestined us to be adopted as sons through Jesus Christ for himself, according to the good pleasure of his will, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"to the praise of his glorious grace "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 1:14","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 5:2","book":"Rom","chapter":5,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 4:15","book":"2Co","chapter":4,"verse":15,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" that he lavished on us in the Beloved One. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 3:17","book":"Mat","chapter":3,"verse":17,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 3:35","book":"Jhn","chapter":3,"verse":35,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 10:17","book":"Jhn","chapter":10,"verse":17,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 1:13","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":13,"letter":"g"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 1:14","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":14},{"label":"Rm 5:2","book":"Rom","chapter":5,"verse":2},{"label":"2Co 4:15","book":"2Co","chapter":4,"verse":15},{"label":"Mt 3:17","book":"Mat","chapter":3,"verse":17},{"label":"Jn 3:35","book":"Jhn","chapter":3,"verse":35},{"label":"Jn 10:17","book":"Jhn","chapter":10,"verse":17},{"label":"Col 1:13","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"In him we have redemption "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 9:12","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" through his blood, the forgiveness "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 25:11","book":"Psa","chapter":25,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 9:2","book":"Mat","chapter":9,"verse":2,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 2:5","book":"Mrk","chapter":2,"verse":5,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 24:47","book":"Luk","chapter":24,"verse":47,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" of our trespasses, according to the riches of his grace "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Heb 9:12","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":12},{"label":"Ps 25:11","book":"Psa","chapter":25,"verse":11},{"label":"Mt 9:2","book":"Mat","chapter":9,"verse":2},{"label":"Mk 2:5","book":"Mrk","chapter":2,"verse":5},{"label":"Lk 24:47","book":"Luk","chapter":24,"verse":47}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"that he richly poured out on us with all wisdom and understanding. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or on us. With all wisdom and understanding"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or on us. With all wisdom and understanding"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He made known to us the mystery of his will, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 11:25","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 16:25","book":"Rom","chapter":16,"verse":25,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 3:3","book":"Eph","chapter":3,"verse":3,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 1:27","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":27,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" according to his good pleasure that he purposed in Christ "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 9:11","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":11,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 11:25","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":25},{"label":"Rm 16:25","book":"Rom","chapter":16,"verse":25},{"label":"Eph 3:3","book":"Eph","chapter":3,"verse":3},{"label":"Col 1:27","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":27},{"label":"Rm 9:11","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"as a plan for the right time "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or the fulfillment of times"},{"kind":"text","text":" —to bring everything together in Christ, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 1:17","book":"Mat","chapter":1,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 5:2","book":"Eph","chapter":5,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" both things in heaven and things on earth "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 2:10","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":10,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" in him. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 1:16","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":16,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 1:17","book":"Mat","chapter":1,"verse":17},{"label":"Eph 5:2","book":"Eph","chapter":5,"verse":2},{"label":"Php 2:10","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":10},{"label":"Col 1:16","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Or the fulfillment of times"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"In him we have also received an inheritance, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or In him we are also an inheritance,"},{"kind":"text","text":" because we were predestined "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 19:21","book":"Pro","chapter":19,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" according to the plan of the one who works out everything in agreement with the purpose of his will, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Pr 19:21","book":"Pro","chapter":19,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or In him we are also an inheritance,"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"so that we who had already put our hope "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 1:3","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" in Christ might bring praise to his glory. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 10:37","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":37,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Th 1:3","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":3},{"label":"Mk 10:37","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":37}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"In him you also were sealed with the promised Holy Spirit "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 51:11","book":"Psa","chapter":51,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 1:33","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":33,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 2:4","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:9","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":9,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 5:25","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":25,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ti 3:5","book":"Tit","chapter":3,"verse":5,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 3:22","book":"Rev","chapter":3,"verse":22,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" when you heard the word of truth, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 1:5","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":5,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Th 2:10","book":"2Th","chapter":2,"verse":10,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"text","text":" the gospel of your salvation, and when you believed. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 51:11","book":"Psa","chapter":51,"verse":11},{"label":"Jn 1:33","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":33},{"label":"Ac 2:4","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":4},{"label":"Rm 8:9","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":9},{"label":"Gl 5:25","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":25},{"label":"Ti 3:5","book":"Tit","chapter":3,"verse":5},{"label":"Rv 3:22","book":"Rev","chapter":3,"verse":22},{"label":"Col 1:5","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":5},{"label":"2Th 2:10","book":"2Th","chapter":2,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The Holy Spirit is the down payment "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 38:17–18","book":"Gen","chapter":38,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 38:20","book":"Gen","chapter":38,"verse":20,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 1:22","book":"2Co","chapter":1,"verse":22,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 5:5","book":"2Co","chapter":5,"verse":5,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" of our inheritance, until the redemption of the possession, to the praise of his glory."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 38:17–18","book":"Gen","chapter":38,"verse":17},{"label":"Gn 38:20","book":"Gen","chapter":38,"verse":20},{"label":"2Co 1:22","book":"2Co","chapter":1,"verse":22},{"label":"2Co 5:5","book":"2Co","chapter":5,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"This is why, since I heard about your faith in the Lord Jesus and your love for all the saints, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I never stop giving thanks for you as I remember you in my prayers. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I pray that the God of our Lord Jesus Christ, the glorious Father, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or the Father of glory"},{"kind":"text","text":" would give you the Spirit "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or a spirit"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 51:12","book":"Psa","chapter":51,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" of wisdom and revelation "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 4:13","book":"1Pe","chapter":4,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" in the knowledge of him. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 51:12","book":"Psa","chapter":51,"verse":12},{"label":"1Pt 4:13","book":"1Pe","chapter":4,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or the Father of glory"},{"marker":2,"text":"Or a spirit"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I pray that the eyes of your heart may be enlightened so that you may know what is the hope "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 1:3","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" of his calling, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 3:15","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":15,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" what is the wealth of his glorious inheritance in the saints, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Th 1:3","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":3},{"label":"Col 3:15","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and what is the immeasurable greatness of his power "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 4:33","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":33,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" toward us who believe, according to the mighty working of his strength."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 4:33","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":33}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He exercised this power in Christ by raising him from the dead and seating him at his right hand "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 2:9","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" in the heavens "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 20:17","book":"Jhn","chapter":20,"verse":17,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 1:3","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 2:6","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":6,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 3:10","book":"Eph","chapter":3,"verse":10,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 6:12","book":"Eph","chapter":6,"verse":12,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 2:10","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":10,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 3:22","book":"1Pe","chapter":3,"verse":22,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" — "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Php 2:9","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":9},{"label":"Jn 20:17","book":"Jhn","chapter":20,"verse":17},{"label":"Eph 1:3","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":3},{"label":"Eph 2:6","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":6},{"label":"Eph 3:10","book":"Eph","chapter":3,"verse":10},{"label":"Eph 6:12","book":"Eph","chapter":6,"verse":12},{"label":"Php 2:10","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":10},{"label":"1Pt 3:22","book":"1Pe","chapter":3,"verse":22}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"far above every ruler and authority, power and dominion, and every title given, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit every name named"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 2:19","book":"2Ti","chapter":2,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" not only in this age but also in the one to come. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 10:30","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":30,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Tm 2:19","book":"2Ti","chapter":2,"verse":19},{"label":"Mk 10:30","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":30}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit every name named"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:1:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And he subjected everything under his feet"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 8:6","book":"Psa","chapter":8,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 8:6","book":"Psa","chapter":8,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 13:1","book":"Rom","chapter":13,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 15:27","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":27,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 3:22","book":"1Pe","chapter":3,"verse":22,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" and appointed him "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Lit gave him"},{"kind":"text","text":" as head "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 2:10","book":"Col","chapter":2,"verse":10,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" over everything for the church, "}],"crossRefs":[{"labe